  "page": {
    "documentTitle": "責任分散 | Concept Reading Lab",
    "bodyClass": "knowledge-page knowledge-diffusion-of-responsibility",
    "heroHtml": "<div class=\"hero-inner\">\n  <div>\n    <p class=\"kicker\">Knowledge Study / ownership / group / inaction</p>\n    <h1>責任分散</h1>\n    <p class=\"topic-subtitle\">Diffusion of Responsibility</p>\n    <p class=\"thesis\">當一件事同時屬於很多人時，它很容易變成實際上誰都沒真的擁有；參與者越多，個人越可能把第一步想成『應該會有人處理』。</p>\n    <div class=\"hero-prompt\">\n      <strong>Read For</strong>\n      <p>這一頁要把『大家都有責任』和『因此誰都不會先動』拆開，因為很多空窗不是缺能力，而是缺明確的第一責任人。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <aside class=\"hero-note\" aria-label=\"主題資訊\">\n    <dl class=\"lexical-meta lexical-meta--knowledge\" aria-label=\"主題摘要\">\n      <div>\n        <dt>主題類型</dt>\n        <dd>群體心理 / 行動稀釋</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>核心問題</dt>\n        <dd>When many people are present, each may feel less personally responsible to act</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>主要判準</dt>\n        <dd>角色清晰度、旁觀者數量、行動門檻、可見性</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>讀完產出</dt>\n        <dd>能在團隊、值班與會議裡更快辨認責任被平均到失真的時刻</dd>\n      </div>\n    </dl>\n    <div class=\"knowledge-map\" aria-label=\"閱讀結構示意\">\n      <span>很多人</span>\n      <span>沒人</span>\n      <span>空窗</span>\n    </div>\n  </aside>\n</div>",
    "mainHtml": "<aside class=\"compass\" aria-label=\"頁內導覽\">\n  <span>Reading Path</span>\n  <a href=\"#core\">讀法總覽</a>\n  <a href=\"#setup\">問題設定</a>\n  <a href=\"#lenses\">判準透鏡</a>\n  <a href=\"#psychology\">心理連結</a>\n  <a href=\"#applications\">現實映射</a>\n  <a href=\"#misreadings\">誤讀校正</a>\n  <a href=\"#questions\">延伸提問</a>\n  <a href=\"#sources\">來源</a>\n</aside>\n\n<article class=\"article\">\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"core\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Orientation</p>\n      <h2>責任一旦被攤太薄，主動性常不是平均分配，而是一起蒸發</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">責任分散提醒你：共享責任若沒有結構化 ownership，很容易退化成集體旁觀。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"core-card\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Core Tension</p>\n      <p>多人參與本來能帶來支援與備援，但若誰該先動、誰該收尾不清楚，群體反而更可能出現行動空窗。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"principle-strip\" aria-label=\"本頁讀法\">\n      <div>\n        <span>01</span>\n        <strong>先把第一步綁到人</strong>\n        <p>越重要的事，越不能只說『大家留意』。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>02</span>\n        <strong>再讓行動可見</strong>\n        <p>若沒人知道別人是否已接手，觀望就會自然蔓延。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>03</span>\n        <strong>最後分清共享與模糊</strong>\n        <p>共享責任需要清楚交接，不是把責任平均稀釋。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"setup\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Setup</p>\n      <h2>從一個所有人都在現場、事情卻還是拖著沒動的時刻開始</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">責任分散在 incident、值班、群組協作與大型會議裡尤其常見。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"definition-grid\">\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>最小劇情</strong>\n        <p>bug 通知發到大群組，大家都看到了，但因為沒指名 owner，最初十分鐘反而沒人真正接住。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>真正難點</strong>\n        <p>人不是故意懶，而是群體情境改寫了每個人對『是不是我該先動』的感受。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"concept-flow\" aria-label=\"問題展開\">\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">多人同時知道一件事</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">個人責任感被稀釋</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">行動空窗出現或拖延放大</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"paradox-frame\">\n      <strong>Key Point</strong>\n      <p>責任分散最常偽裝成『大家都在關心』，但真正缺的是誰在負責。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"lenses\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Lenses</p>\n      <h2>四個看 ownership 稀釋的角度</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">只要你看到一件事人人有份、人人模糊，就值得懷疑責任分散正在發生。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"lens-grid\">\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>指派明確度</strong>\n        <p>是否有清楚 owner，而不是一個模糊的『各位請處理』？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>狀態可見性</strong>\n        <p>大家看得出來誰已接手、處理到哪裡嗎？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>行動門檻</strong>\n        <p>要開始處理是否需要太多請示或確認？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>群體規模</strong>\n        <p>參與者越多、角色越重疊，責任越容易被平均到看不見。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>場景</th>\n            <th>責任分散看起來像</th>\n            <th>後果</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>大群組通知</td>\n            <td>大家都看到了</td>\n            <td>最初無人真正接手</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>會議待辦</td>\n            <td>共識是要做</td>\n            <td>會後沒有明確 owner 便自然蒸發</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>值班升級</td>\n            <td>有很多人在線</td>\n            <td>每個人都以為別人已經在處理</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"psychology\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Psychology</p>\n      <h2>為什麼人一多，主動性反而可能下降</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">因為當責任不再明確落在自己身上時，觀望就會被合理化成正常等待。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>他人存在會降低緊迫感</strong>\n        <p>只要還有很多人也知道，個人就更容易先等等看。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>不確定誰該動</strong>\n        <p>角色模糊時，出手本身反而像冒進。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>共享關注會被誤讀成共享處理</strong>\n        <p>大家都 aware，不代表大家都在 act。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"micro-note\">責任分散不是人變冷漠，而是群體結構改變了責任感的落點。</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"applications\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Applications</p>\n      <h2>把 ownership 補回事件處理與協作流程</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">對工程團隊來說，責任分散最常讓 incident、待辦和跨團隊依賴在『大家都知道』中悄悄失速。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>Incident command</strong>\n        <p>重大事件若沒有明確指揮與分工，很容易一堆人在線卻沒有有效推進。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>PR review</strong>\n        <p>指派 reviewers 很多不代表 review 會更快，反而可能人人等別人先看。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>跨部門跟進</strong>\n        <p>只把議題留在共同 Slack 頻道，常比指定 owner 更容易掉。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"bullet-list\">\n      <li>『大家留意』幾乎等於沒指派；關鍵事項最好永遠落到名字而不是群體。</li>\n      <li>越多人參與的流程，越需要狀態可見與 ownership 轉移規則。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"misreadings\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Misreadings</p>\n      <h2>三個常見誤讀</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">責任分散不是說團隊合作不好，而是說合作需要結構化責任。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"collocation-list\" aria-label=\"常見誤讀\">\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>人多就一定沒效率</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>不是。問題在於責任有沒有被清楚配置。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>這和偷懶一樣</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>很多時候是 ownership 設計失敗，不是動機低。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>只在旁觀者效應才有</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>現代團隊協作與線上溝通一樣常見。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"questions\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Questions</p>\n      <h2>這件事現在是真的有人接住，還是只是很多人都知道</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">下面兩個問題很適合放在會後與 incident 中。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prompt-grid\">\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>如果現在要追進度，我能直接說出負責的名字嗎</strong>\n        <p>答不出來時，多半就是責任已被稀釋。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>參與者增加時，ownership 有沒有變得更清楚，還是更模糊</strong>\n        <p>答案會直接影響行動速度。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"template-note\">\n      <strong>延伸路線</strong>\n      <p>延伸閱讀可接 bystander effect、social loafing 與 ownership design。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"sources\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Sources</p>\n      <h2>來源與整理方式</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">這一頁以 diffusion of responsibility 為主，再把概念帶回群組協作、incident 與 ownership 設計。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"source-grid\">\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>主概念</strong>\n        <p>Diffusion of responsibility 條目整理了多人在場時個人責任感如何被稀釋。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diffusion_of_responsibility\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Diffusion of Responsibility</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>相鄰概念</strong>\n        <p>Bystander effect 可作為對照，理解群體旁觀如何出現。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bystander_effect\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Bystander Effect</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>近鄰效應</strong>\n        <p>Social loafing 有助於理解群體情境如何改變投入與主動性。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_loafing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Social Loafing</a>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\">\n    <div class=\"reference-box\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"section-label\">Reference</p>\n        <h2>下一步</h2>\n        <p>讀完後可以看一條你們最常靠群組追的流程，檢查它是否真的有明確第一責任人。</p>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"reference-link\" href=\"../knowledge-topic-template.html\">打開模板</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</article>"
  }
